txt.en: 'Don't you have some vegetables to cook?'
Execute the recipe for par-cooked vegetables ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
The crafting recipes you must create can be found in your crafting panel.\n\nCook twenty-five servings of par-cooked vegetables.
'I think this new farming technique shows promise. The results certainly speak for themselves.'
Talk to the Cook's Guild Leader in Minas Morgul
'I think this new farming technique shows promise. The results certainly speak for themselves.'
'Don't you have some vegetables to cook?'
'I hear farmers are growing different types of vegetables mixed together in the field. I wonder if they taste good eaten together! Do me a favour and prepare a few servings.'
Executed the recipe for par-cooked vegetables ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
'I hear farmers are growing different types of vegetables mixed together in the field. I wonder if they taste good eaten together! Do me a favour and prepare a few servings.'
The leader of the Cook's Guild would like to see how you would prepare mixed vegetables.
